Author: bananacustardcream
Text: Oh, definitely. I used to think that stopping mid-binge was plain impossible for me!

Author: silvernikki
Text: I've done this so many times. If you feel like looking for the bright side -- at least you were aware enough to stop the binge. Even if your resolve isn't *strong* yet, at least it's *stronger*. At least that's what I tell myself.
